<p>Once you have a degree or equivalent qualification you’re ready for postgraduate primary or secondary initial teacher training courses.</p>

<p>You also need the following GCSEs at grade 4 (C) or above, or equivalent qualifications:</p>

<ul>
  <li>English</li>
  <li>maths</li>
  <li>science if you want to teach primary</li>
</ul>

<p>You may be able to show you meet the standard in another way if you do not have GCSEs.</p>

